AI "brains" help the platform to outsource the thinking on which is the best way to source the funds needed for a
specific spending.

Localized "brains" may find optimized ways to source the funds and in that way producing a better performance for the
end user. "brains" may take into account taxing implications in different jurisdictions to optimize their results.

The platform will run all "brains" available and apply the resulting calculations of the most convenient one.
